commands.name: az logic integration-account partner create
commands.syntax:
az logic integration-account partner create --content
                                            --integration-account-name
                                            --name
                                            --partner-type {B2B, NotSpecified}
                                            --resource-group
                                            [--location]
                                            [--metadata]
                                            [--tags]
examples: az logic integration-account partner create -g rg -n partner --integration-account-name name --content '{b2b:{businessIdentities:[{qualifier:AA,value:BB}]}}' --partner-type B2B

commands.name: az logic integration-account partner delete
examples: az logic integration-account partner delete -g rg -n partner --integration-account-name name

commands.name: az logic integration-account partner list
examples: az logic integration-account partner list -g rg --integration-account-name name

commands.name: az logic integration-account partner show
examples: az logic integration-account partner show -g rg -n partner --integration-account-name name

commands.name: az logic integration-account partner update
commands.syntax:
az logic integration-account partner update [--add]
                                            [--content]
                                            [--force-string {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                            [--ids]
                                            [--integration-account-name]
                                            [--location]
                                            [--metadata]
                                            [--name]
                                            [--partner-type {B2B, NotSpecified}]
                                            [--remove]
                                            [--resource-group]
                                            [--set]
                                            [--subscription]
                                            [--tags]
examples: az logic integration-account partner update -g rg -n partner --integration-account-name name --content '{b2b:{businessIdentities:[{qualifier:CC,value:DD}]}}'
